{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Structure","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSSwitchItemV","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"symbolKind":"struct","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSwitchItem"}],"title":"OUDSSwitchItem"},"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/init(_:isOn:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:isReadOnly:hasDivider:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/body"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsswitchitem"]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some swith components."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a switch with only an indicator, prefer instead "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitch"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Layouts","type":"heading","anchor":"Layouts"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"inverse"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing switch indicator and a leading optional decorative icon"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"text":"Indicator states","type":"heading","anchor":"Indicator-states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The switch indicator has two available states set as a boolean property that determines whether the toggle is on or off."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as disabled."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The switch can be also outlined in some cases."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom switch trait.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Forbidden by design","type":"heading","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}]}]},{"level":2,"text":"Code samples","type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, helper: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading switch with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\", helper: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an additonal label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\",","                   helper: \"1967\",","                   isReversed: true,","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an helper text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   helper: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                   isReversed: true,","                   isError: true,","                   hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\", isOn: $isOn)","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related switch as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"level":2,"text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/18acc0-switch"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Themes rendering","type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"level":3,"text":"Orange","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchItem_Orange"}]},{"level":3,"text":"Orange Business Tools","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchItem_OrangeBusinessTools"}]},{"level":3,"text":"Orange Inverse","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Inverse"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_switchItem_OrangeInverse","type":"image"}]},{"level":3,"text":"Sosh","type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchItem_Sosh"}]},{"level":3,"text":"Wireframe","type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_switchItem_Wireframe","type":"image"}]},{"style":"note","name":"Version","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.1.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"type":"aside"},{"style":"note","name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.14.0","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSwitchItem":{"navigatorTitle":